<%- include ../Partials/header.ejs %>
<%- include ../Partials/main_nav.ejs %>

<head>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/Content/faq.css' />
    <script src="/Scripts/faq.js" defer></script>
</head>

<main>
    <section class="FAQs">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h1>

        <!-- Accordion Item 1 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <div class="accordion-header">
                <h2>What is the purpose of this application?</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-content">
                <p>This application helps you manage your to-do list efficiently by allowing you to add, edit, delete, and track tasks.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Accordion Item 2 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <div class="accordion-header">
                <h2>How do I add a task?</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-content">
                <p>You can add a task by clicking on the "Add Task" button on your home page. Fill in the task details and click "Save."</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Accordion Item 3 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <div class="accordion-header">
                <h2>How can I change the status of a task?</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-content">
                <p>You can change the status of a task by editing it from the to-do list page. Select the task, update the status, and save the changes."</p>
            </div>
        </div>


     <!-- Accordion Item 4 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <div class="accordion-header">
                <h2>How can I change the delete a task?</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-content">
                <p>You can delete any task by clicking on the "Delete" button next to it in the to-do list."</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Accordion Item 5 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <div class="accordion-header">
                <h2>How do I log in to my account?</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-content">
                <p>You can log in by clicking the "Log In" button in the navigation bar. Enter the credentials (username and password) on the login page to access your account."</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Accordion Item 6 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <div class="accordion-header">
                <h2>Is my data saved when I log out?</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-content">
                <p>Yes, all your tasks and data are saved in the system, evening after you log out. You can log back in at any time to view or update your tasks."</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    
    </section>
</main>


